Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.26,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使如此  我也想擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}巨大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:47.18,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在這裡  從此起步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.06,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我明白的  不淨是快樂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.15,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這是在考驗我們吧  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.07,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為  這份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.11,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會讓我們通往未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:02.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家齊心協力能讓自己變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不斷的變化  We'll be star!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能為自己所喜歡的事加油的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:16.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就以新目的地為目標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:21.34,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能堅信自己所喜歡的事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:26.43,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就懷揣這份雀躍感前進吧
