Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:34.33,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要大家期望  那就能夠做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:37.29,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比誰都要努力
