Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.74,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちの思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:48.41,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}集まれば  何とかなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.71,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}小さな力だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.54,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}育てたい夢がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.72,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}わからないことだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.47,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ポケットに  地図なんて持ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}少しずつでもいいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.56,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}胸張って進もうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.56,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}躓いたら脱する
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.48,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}笑ってみる笑顔で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}わい  わい  わい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:24.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大丈夫  飾らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.95,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}素直な声で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}1234  みんな  Go today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.96,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Someday いつの日か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.05,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}叶うよ  願いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:43.05,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Someday いつの日か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.01,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}届くと信じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:51.27,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう  泣いてなんかいられないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.56,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だって  さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}楽しみはまだまだまだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.65,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}これから！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----INlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.74,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大家的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:48.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}彙集起來就能有所作為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.71,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然只是小小的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.54,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但也有想要實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.72,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然盡是未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.47,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}即使口袋裡沒有地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但只要一步步地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.56,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}挺起胸膛前進就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.56,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}摔倒了就馬上站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.48,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綻放出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大聲歡呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:24.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}沒關係的  用不經修飾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}率直的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}1234  大家  Go today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.96,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Someday  總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.05,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願望將會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:43.05,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Someday  總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.01,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我堅信會傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:51.27,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}對  怎麼能夠哭哭啼啼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.56,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}因為  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}快樂的事還有那麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.65,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}都在等著我們！
